    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pigment comprising colored molecules synthesized by photosynthetic organisms. Natural organic dyes and colorants may be obtained from the stems, roots, and flowers of plants. Colored materials from plants have been used by humans since ancient times.</Note_Text>
